title: For Sale/Trade:  K&K P30SK V3
postcontent: I have a Heckler & Koch (H&K) P30SK (Sub Kompact) with the V3 trigger. Looked long and hard to find it! I originally bought it after picking one up in a gun store and being amazed by the grip ergonomics. What sent me back to buy was learning about the trigger system. V3 trigger is double action 1st shot, then single action thereafter AND a deckocker so you can carry hammer down on a round. Think of it as the trigger system you wish your 1911's had. The absolute best of all worlds! Shoots better than any Glock, Sig, Springfield, etc I've owned (trigger, low recoil, dead on accuracy). BUT...I've recently gotten addicted to saving $. Just keeping my pocket piece and using this one to grow my cash.- Original hard case with papers, back straps, side panels, etc.- Two mags. I bought the H&K pinky extensions for both. They are textured just like the grip. H&K does not offer these anymore. All of the other pinky extensions available do not match the guns texture!- Shown right hand draw, in waist DeSantis holster is also available. If you want it, add $25.Will sell without holster for $600 cash FIRM (Save lower offers please). I prefer cash, but may take a trade (weighed heavily in my favor) with at least $200 cash.
